parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine failure, causing the vehicle to stall or seize while driving, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or seize while driving, resulting in accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Vacuum pump failure can cause engine failure, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Camshaft seal failure can cause engine failure, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Unexplained engine fire can cause damage to the vehicle and surrounding property, and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Smoke emanating from the engine compartment

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ingress of moisture into the headlight assembly can cause the headlight to malfunction or fail, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Water or condensation inside the headlight assembly

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design and performance issues with the headlights can cause reduced visibility, glare, and discomfort for oncoming drivers, increasing the risk of accidents.
The inadequate performance of the backup lights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries when reversing.
symptoms: Dim or inadequate backup light performance
inability to see objects or vehicles behind the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag red light indicator remains on for an extended period

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the anti-theft system can cause the doors to become stuck, trapping occupants inside the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The doors will not unlock from the inside
and the occupants become trapped inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlight assembly can cause the loss of headlights, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Condensation or water enters the headlight housing
causing the ballast and bulb to fail
resulting in a loss of headlights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the dashboard and radio to malfunction, leading to a loss of critical vehicle functions and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard and radio go out completely
even if only for a brief period.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the remote keyless entry system can cause the doors to become stuck, trapping occupants inside the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The doors will not open with the remote
causing the doors to lock and trapping occupants inside the vehicle.
